<mvc:View controllerName="journeyPlanner.JourneyPlanner.controller.Worklist" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:semantic="sap.m.semantic">
	<Page title="Smart Journey Planner">
		<content>
			<GenericTile header="Real Time Journey Planner"
			    class="sapUiLargeMarginBegin sapUiLargeMarginTop smartJourneyPlannerWorklistTiles" 
				busyIndicatorDelay="{worklistView>/tableBusyDelay}" 
				press="onRealTimeTilePress" 
				backgroundImage="images/RealTimeCrowd.jpg">
			</GenericTile>
			<GenericTile header="Historical Journey Planner" 
			    class="sapUiMediumMarginBegin sapUiLargeMarginTop smartJourneyPlannerWorklistTiles" 
				busyIndicatorDelay="{worklistView>/tableBusyDelay}" 
				press="onHistoryTilePress" 
				backgroundImage="images/HistoricalCrowd.jpg">
			</GenericTile>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>